data.description: Welcome to 116 Buck Mountain Road!! This beautiful SPLIT-LEVEL home sits on 2 ACRES of PRISTINE land with a THREE STALL BARN located at the back of the property. Did we mention this beauty is NOT LOCATED IN AN HOA? Come check out this SECLUDED home--located in WEATHERLY SCHOOL DISTRICT! The layout of the home also suits anyone looking for a possible IN-LAW SUITE. With full living areas, full kitchens, full bathrooms, and bedrooms located on both levels of the home--ideal for anyone looking for a lot of space! The SPACIOUS TWO CAR GARAGE leaves ample room for INSIDE PARKING and storage. Come see it before it's gone!
